reviewText: If you want a fun steam-punk movie. This was it. I felt with was worth the purchase price and would buy the DVD if it weren't available through Amazon
Freaky movie. I didn't make it 15 min. in, but okay none the less.

Caught this one for free on the web,  liked it enough to buy the dvd,  The costuming and cinematography are pretty good, the dialog and acting took a little bit of time to warm up to, but found the whole thing to be a fun little romp in a retro future!  Like much of scifi, it has the feel of Metropolis,
